le for paying this charge<br />\n<br />\nLate/unpaid/returned rent payments: \u00a330 per week late payment charge and 3% above the base rate of Bank of England per annum, calculated daily<br />\n<br />\nTenant Swap: \u00a3420 administration fee + references<br />\n<br />\nRenewal: \u00a3210 for each renewal.<br />\n<br />\nChanging tenancy documents once signed: \u00a3150 <br />\n<br />\nEarly termination (at landlord s discretion) All costs incurred by the landlord for allowing early termination including the agent's existing or re-letting fees<br />\n<br />\nStamp Duty Land Tax payable on tenancies where the rent exceeds \u00a3125,000\n",
